snippet.title: Pinball FX Arrived to Xbox, PlayStation and the Epic Games Store!
snippet.description:
There’s a pinball game for everybody – and we’re releasing more than 80 tables at launch to prove it. 

Many are based on your favorite brands: Marvel. Star Wars. The Addams Family. Borderlands. Snoopy. Garfield. DreamWorks Animation. Jurassic World. Indiana Jones. Others bring home real-world pinball classics from Williams, or they’re pure Zen originals. 

Play Today: 
Xbox: https://bit.ly/PinballFX_PlayOnXboxYT
PlayStation: https://bit.ly/PinballFX_PlayOnPlayStationYT
Epic Games Store: https://bit.ly/PinballFX_PlayOnEpicGamesYT

Join the Zenthusiast mailing list to get news and discount info!
http://eepurl.com/dqZJgn

Join the Pinball FX Discord to dish it out with other pinball fans!
http://bit.ly/pfxdiscord
